    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ANSWER CAPSULE: Quick Reference -->
  <section style="padding: 32px 1.5rem; background: #f0f7ff; border-bottom: 2px solid var(--blue);">
    <div style="max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto;">
      <p style="color: var(--navy); font-size: 0.95rem; line-height: 1.7;"><strong>Angel Bail Bonds provides 24/7 bail bond services for Garfield County, Oklahoma. The Garfield County Detention Center is located at 1020 S 10th Street, Enid, OK 73701. Call (405) 614-3000 to begin the bail process. The detention center phone number is (580) 548-2429. The facility holds up to 204 inmates, is staffed by 99 officers, and processes approximately 880 bookings per year. Most inmates are released 2-6 hours after the bond is posted. We accept cash, Visa, Mastercard, Zelle, Venmo, and offer financing.</strong></p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FACILITY + STEPS — combined, two-column -->
  <section style="padding: 48px 1.5rem; background: white;">
